data.description: This beautiful HistoryMaker Home could be yours. This 3 bedroom, 2 & 1/2 bath, two-story home is like new and in excellent condition. This home comes with the refrigerator, washer, and dryer. It is still under the builders two year home warranty until February 2024, and 10 year until February 2032. Featuring full yard sprinkler system, dual zoned AC, climate controlled attic with dehumidifier, storm shutters, and gutters around the front of the home, this home also includes low-e insulated windows, and other energy-saving features. Artesia Village connects to the La Porte by the Bay hike and bike trails, is near the Bay Forest Golf Course, and is just minutes from the Little Cedar Bayou Park. Don’t wait because there are only a few available homes left in this neighborhood, conveniently located off of 146. Schedule your tour today.
